name: Department of Human Services
directions: Ask the receptionist to use a single-user restroom if needed. Lobby multi-stall bathrooms are gendered with a sign encouraging folx to use the restroom in accordance with their gender identity or a single-user restroom upon request. The single user restroom is not accessible without going through a secure area in the building.

name: Department of Human Services
directions: Individual single stall restroom available upon request (only single stall restroom is available in a secure part of the building).

I also don't know if they'd let non-customers use it, but they seem really nice there and I bet if you asked they would let you. There's a Dunkin right next door though, which is bound to have gendered bathrooms at least.
